\id GAL - Ampeele NT [apz] -Papua New Guinea 1988 (web version -2012 bd) 
\h Ngkolesiya 
\toc1 Olo Iyoswo loso Poul AÍûåamu Ngkolesiya somneÍûåno Mt…®Íûåmokumentisofoho. 
